553
00:41:37,399 --> 00:41:40,799
The guys from Tiele Tribe, why do you fear the Ashile Tribe so much?

554
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:45,659
Monan and Mobei proposed to unite because you need more courage from us.

555
00:41:45,659 --> 00:41:47,439
Great Tang has just won the race,

556
