557
00:41:49,999 --> 00:41:53,339
Obviously, they want us to make a choice in front of the people from the Ashile Tribe.

558
00:41:53,339 --> 00:41:56,679
Doing it like this, won't Great Tang become the next Ashile Tribe to us?

559
00:41:56,679 --> 00:41:58,180
You...

560
