562
00:42:01,540 --> 00:42:03,700
Don't stop me.

563
00:42:05,620 --> 00:42:07,500
Changge.

564
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:12,359
Everybody, the Emperor of Tang means that once Tang is by your side,

565
00:42:12,359 --> 00:42:14,580
